Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的所有活动都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位执行委员到放映室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那接下来要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意好  JUNES王子请客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  让两位选美冠军请客怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想让女孩子请客  真是过分啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要击穿你的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自称女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请不要再提大赛的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们就这么解散的话也太没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  原来你来参观文化祭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我吃过炒面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跳了舞  玩了鬼屋  还去占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去占卜过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  一个漂亮的姐姐说哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  小…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说我是小…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说你是天生的小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找过你了  但总是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一大早我就要出差去县厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜我就得动身了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你和菜菜子看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  学长要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子一个人也能看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那菜菜子今晚要不要住我家的店里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？哎！小雪你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问她要不要住我家的店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅馆开个庆祝会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  但是  菜菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  太棒啊  住旅馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是请菜菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃得到温泉鸡蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住一晚吧  那我得先和爷爷说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉  浴衣  盛开的鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是直斗  爷爷在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是去干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住旅馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会来  很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家在家里准备好之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就集体在天城屋旅馆集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是先回一趟家再出门…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西小姐  要给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么多人真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢  我们久候各位多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  小雪是温泉旅馆未来的老板娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我只是个女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  突然来了一群团体客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪  难得有朋友来  你明明可以全都交给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会结束之前还需要人手对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来领各位去房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托…了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她时不时会过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时来帮忙的话  爱家那边怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题的  请到房间去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色调是不是有些太鲜艳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可能浅一些  能让人放松的那种比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得学姐好帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花的数量也稍微减少些…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家没住同一个房间啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁的话我就忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她们的房间也离得太远了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么空房了  所以女生的房间好像在另一层
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这半年来我们还真是经常在一起过夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐篷  酒店  还有旅馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服换的真快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好饱好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好满足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好幸福啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打扑克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生们说要去泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是混浴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢泡好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡前去泡一下就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来这个房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是挺高档的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你也很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说旺季中这种房间怎么可能会空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是故意装作不知道罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里说不定发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家为什么都一声不吭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去接接看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长们害怕个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天浴场现在好像没什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起洗澡  真让人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:27.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,350)\3c88B4E7\bord6\fsp1}熊熊的想象画面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:27.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,350)\3c1E3B8E\bord3\fsp1}熊熊的想象画面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐向同一个方向互相擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者会边看富士山边唱歌对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的世界充满了开心的事情啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也都多亏了老师啊  谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  电梯到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,42)\fs20\1c202A42\bord0\shad0\b1}露天浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,42)\fs20\1c202A42\bord0\shad0\b1}大浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗同学  过来吧  这边地方很大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗的皮肤真光滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  摸上去滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  皮肤又白头发又柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在摸什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像这样住在外面没问题吗  不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时在哥哥回家前  我一直都是一个人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很会看家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在家的话碰到陌生人敲门不能开门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些道理我是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说菜菜子  要不要试着游游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就一直在游
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也会在这里游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快否定啊  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来比谁先游到那边的水潭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉的人要请客喝水果牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝弹珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我也要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这浴场真大啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一展身手来个熊扒式吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为为为什么你们会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗  呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候就要鼓起勇气  留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这种勇气究竟有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们撤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼行为可是违法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下可得好好教训教训他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  打中了好多下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我很准对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有被看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里在这个时间段是供男性使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄错时间了  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说什么「啊哈哈」  不是吧
